data.description: *100% VA and FHA Financing Available * Newly Built 4BR/2BA Ranch Home Nestled back on .75 Acre Lot. Open One-Level Floor Plan with Bright Open Kitchen with Large Granite Island, Espresso-Stained Cabinets, Backsplash, Stainless Appliances with Side-by-Side Refrigerator, Recessed Lighting, and Eat-In Kitchen Dining. Walk-in Pantry, Laundry/Mud Room with Washer and Dryer included! Large Family Room with Recessed Lighting, and Built-in Entertainment Amour with Wood Accent Inlay. Owners Suite on Main with Walk-In Closet, Double Vanity, Framed Mirrors, HUGE 5x4 Walk-in Shower with Glass Enclosure and Wood Vinyl Tile Surround. , Drop-in Garden Soaking Tub with Wood Accent Inlay! Split Bedroom plan with Three Addition Secondary Bedrooms and Full Bathroom. Large Front Entertaining Deck, and a 10x21 Storage Building Included. Highspeed Internet with ETC. Recently Paved Driveway! Great Location Close to Shopping and Dining (15 min) Ellijay and East Ellijay (10 min) Carters Lake (28 Min) Blue Ridge.
